00:48:45.200 --> 00:48:46.940
in this journey of
customer centricity--

00:48:46.940 --> 00:48:48.920
I've had the
opportunity to interview

00:48:48.920 --> 00:48:51.154
a lot of folks in
the business world

00:48:51.154 --> 00:48:52.820
when we were putting
the book together--

00:48:52.820 --> 00:48:54.830
Pete and I are writing
articles, currently--

00:48:54.830 --> 00:48:57.080
also putting this
