00:51:15.790 --> 00:51:18.010
What would be a couple
of key questions

00:51:18.010 --> 00:51:22.150
that we can ask our clients
to identify those components

00:51:22.150 --> 00:51:23.630
for their business models?

00:51:23.630 --> 00:51:24.380
PETER FADER: Sure.

00:51:24.380 --> 00:51:27.670
I really have to say that
moving the conversation

00:51:27.670 --> 00:51:30.190
over too early-- starting the
conversation with the folks

00:51:30.190 --> 00:51:33.220
