00:51:52.570 --> 00:51:55.180
late-stage VCs, who are
looking at a company they

00:51:55.180 --> 00:51:56.350
want to acquire.

00:51:56.350 --> 00:51:58.120
But it becomes
really interesting

00:51:58.120 --> 00:52:01.104
when we're looking at a company,
