of the value of our customers?

00:52:12.440 --> 00:52:14.192
So they can come up
with the number--

00:52:14.192 --> 00:52:16.150
hopefully higher than
what Wall Street thinks--

00:52:16.150 --> 00:52:18.580
and then make a whole
big deal about it,

00:52:18.580 --> 00:52:22.047
not only that the number is
