00:53:31.590 --> 00:53:33.900
have that incremental
dollar to spend,

00:53:33.900 --> 00:53:36.210
Byron Sharp says,
grow your base.

00:53:36.210 --> 00:53:38.460
You must have more buyers.

00:53:38.460 --> 00:53:40.530
I agree, but for a
different reason.

00:53:40.530 --> 00:53:42.970
I say, let's focus
more on acquisition.

00:53:42.970 --> 00:53:45.232
Let's go out there and find
