Now there are some differences.

00:53:51.780 --> 00:53:53.940
And I have the ultimate
love-hate relationship

00:53:53.940 --> 00:53:57.010
with Byron Sharp.

00:53:57.010 --> 00:54:01.650
And just to kind of summarize
the biggest difference,

00:54:01.650 --> 00:54:03.960
the CLV distribution
that I showed--

00:54:03.960 --> 00:54:06.870
the fact that we got this tail
of people out there that sticks

00:54:06.870 --> 00:54:07.370
