He believes that-- it's not so--

00:54:16.050 --> 00:54:18.390
he believes in
heterogeneity, but not

00:54:18.390 --> 00:54:21.480
that there's as
much of a skew to it

00:54:21.480 --> 00:54:23.830
as we see in the actual data.

00:54:23.830 --> 00:54:26.940
So a lot of my career has been
taking the kinds of models

00:54:26.940 --> 00:54:30.420
